  <brief_title>Plethysmography Variability Index Monitoring for Parturients With Antepartum Hemorrhage</brief_title>
  <official_title>Continuous Non Invasive Monitoring of Both Plethysmography Variability Index and Total Hemoglobin During Cesarean Section for Antepartum Hemorrhage As a Method For Early Detection of Bleeding</official_title>
  <sponsors>
