  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the use of continuous noninvasive intraoperative
      plethesmography variability index in conjunction with Hemoglobin levels monitoring using
      Masimo Radical-7™ Pulse CO-Oximeter during elective cesarean sections in patients with
      antepartum and intrapartum hemorrhage as a guide for fluid and blood transfusion practice .
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
